\v 17-18 It…®mah Iesu …ôp…ôha il…®s e n…®t…ôu…ôt r…ôha Uhg…®n nian Uhg…®n Tat…ô t…ôm…ôf…ôn n…®siai…ôn k…ôm in, k…ôni mol in n…ôhag…ôhagi…ôn tasi…ô miet e n…®p…ôt…®n, k…ôni t…ôm…ôt…ôu n…ôuia Uhg…®n u N…ôhag…ôhagi…ôn Asoli t…ôm…ôni k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúInu n…ôt…®k i…ôt…ôm i…ôkolkeikei, n…®kik tagi…ôn p…®k ohni.‚Äù It…®mahal m…®n i…ômhl…ôt…ôu n…ôuian …ôha t…ôms…®p…ôn e neg…ôu e neai.\x - \xo 1:17-18 \xt Mat 17:5; Mak 9:7; Luk 9:35\x*
