\v 6 K…ôni Uhg…®n t…ômol nalp…®ni…ôn o n…ôrahi…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôm Sot…ôm m…®ne K…ômor…ô, k…ôni t…ômuvan taun mil …ôha e n…®g…ôm, kuol n…ôhmtahu e lau. Inu t…ôt…ôg…ôtun nati nak i…ôt…ôm otol k…ôm n…ôt…ômimi m…®n u n…ôt…ôm kaut…ôhti n…ôuian.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jen 19:24; Jut 7\x*
\v 7 M…ôt…ôu in t…ômosmi…ôg…ôh i…ôt…ômi u Lot. In i…ôt…ômi …ôhruahru e n…ôhmt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôni n…®kin t…ôtahm…ô o noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n i…ôt…ôm tol naul…®si…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ômi m…®n …ôha ik…®n …ôha u k…ômaut…ôhti n…ôuia Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jen 19:1-16\x*
\v 8 K…ôni in t…ôm…ôtat…®g ilah min ilah, k…ôni nian r…ôfin in t…ômeruh noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n r…ôhalah, k…ôni m…ôt…ôt…ôu n…ôghati…ôn t…ôrah m…®n r…ôhalah, k…ôni nian r…ôfin …ôm…ô, n…®kin i…ôt…ôm t…ôhruahru …ôm…ô, t…ômahm…ô p…®k o noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n r…ôhalah.
\p 
